---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="container page-wrapper py-8 animate-fade-in mx-auto">
    <header class="mb-8 text-center mt-4">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-slate-800 tracking-tight">お問い合わせ</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3 font-medium">ご意見、ご感想、解説の誤りのご指摘などをお寄せください。</p>
    </header>

    <main class="bg-white p-6 sm:p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 text-center">
      
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-medium mb-10 text-sm sm:text-base">
        ご意見・ご感想・解説の誤りのご指摘などはGoogleフォームよりお気軽にお送りください。<br class="hidden sm:inline" />いただいたご意見はサイト改善に活用させていただきます。
      </p>

      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <a href="https://forms.gle/r5kPrm1RhbxyKwUo8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary-lg">
          <span>お問い合わせはこちら</span>
        </a>
      </div>

    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .btn-primary-lg {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, #0284c7 100%);
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.35);
    transition: transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1), box-shadow 0.2s;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 360px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .btn-primary-lg:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.45);
  }
  
  .btn-primary-lg:active {
    transform: translateY(2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3);
  }
</style>
